## Basic flextable {  }

### Create a flextable {.unnumbered}  

To create and manage **flextable** objects, we first pass the data frame through the `flextable()` function. We save the result as `my_table`.  


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
my_table <- flextable(table) 
my_table
```

