### Font and alignment {.unnumbered}

We centre-align all columns aside from the left-most column with the hospital names, using the `align()` function from **flextable**.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
my_table <- my_table %>% 
   flextable::align(align = "center", j = c(2:8), part = "all") 
my_table
```

